  </div>

  <!-- Course Detail Main Section -->
<main class="course-detail-grid">
  <!-- Left Content -->
  <section class="course-left">
    <CourseIcon 
    width="60" 
    height="60" 
    style="flex: none; order: 0; flex-grow: 0; margin-bottom: 16px;" 
   />
    <h2>Scrum Master Course</h2>
    <p>09/18 - 11/14</p>
    <p>Brookline, MA</p>
    <button class="register-btn">Register</button>

    <h3>ABOUT THIS COURSE</h3>
    <p style="text-align: justify;">This intensive Scrum Master course delves into the core principles and practices of the Scrum framework, providing a comprehensive understanding of the Scrum Master's role as a servant leader within an Agile environment. Through a blend of instruction, interactive exercises, real-world case studies, and discussions, participants will gain practical insights into facilitating Scrum events (Sprint Planning, Daily Scrum, Sprint Review, and Retrospective), coaching development teams, managing the Product Backlog, and effectively removing impediments to ensure successful project outcomes.</p>

    <h3>WHAT YOU’LL LEARN</h3>
    <p style="text-align: justify;">The program aims to equip individuals with the knowledge and skills necessary to foster team collaboration, promote continuous improvement, and drive Agile adoption within their organizations across diverse industries. This course is suitable for anyone involved in product delivery using Scrum, including aspiring Scrum Masters, Agile coaches, managers, and team members seeking to enhance their Agile capabilities.</p>

    <h3>MEET THE INSTRUCTORS</h3>
    <div class="instructors-icons">
      <div class="instructor-icon">😀 John Doe</div>
      <div class="instructor-icon">😀 Walter White</div>
      <div class="instructor-icon">😀 Jane Smith</div>
    </div>

    <h3>PMI</h3>
    <!-- <p>[...]</p> -->

    <button class="register-btn">Register</button>
  </section>

  <!-- Right Sidebar -->
  <aside class="course-right">
    <p>Length: <strong>2 months</strong></p>
    <p>Effort: <strong>Intermediate</strong></p>
    <p>Price: <strong>USD 499.00</strong></p>

    <h3>REVIEWS</h3>
    <div class="review-card">
  <ReviewIcon class="review-icon" />
  <p>The Scrum Master certification training by SCRUMstudy was transformative for a career. The course content was comprehensive.</p>
</div>
    <div class="review-card">
  <ReviewIcon class="review-icon" />
  <p>The Certified ScrumMaster (CSM) course taught by Eric Tucker was a very positive experience.</p>
</div>
    <div class="review-card">
  <ReviewIcon class="review-icon" />
  <p>This class was a relevant step in learning more about being a better scrum master and the journey in front of the scrum master.
  </p>
</div>

